.TH TOPIC OLC 
.UC
.SH COMMAND 
topic \- display or list topics
.SH USAGE
.B topic 
.B [\-list] [\-file <file name>]
.br
.SH DESCRIPTION
When this command is used with no arguments, the topic of the current
conversation is displayed.
.PP
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-list
List all OLC topics. 
.TP
.B \-file
Specify a file for output. Only useful in conjunction with the
.I \-list
option.
